<!-- SERVICES -->
<section id="services">
  <p class="section-label">// What We Do</p>
  <h2 class="section-title">Full-stack AI implementation.</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">From environment setup to production automation — we handle the entire AI stack so your team can focus on building.</p>

  <div class="services-grid">
    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">&gt;_</div>
      <h3>Claude Code Setup</h3>
      <p>Full environment configuration — permissions, project context, custom commands, and terminal integration. Your developers get a coding co-pilot that actually understands your codebase from day one.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">⬡</div>
      <h3>MCP Server Implementation</h3>
      <p>We connect Claude to your tools — Slack, GitHub, Drive, Salesforce, Jira, databases, and more. Proper authentication, scoping, and data flow so Claude can read and act on your company's real information.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">{'{ }'}</div>
      <h3>API Integration</h3>
      <p>Custom Anthropic API integrations for your product or internal tools. Structured outputs, streaming, function calling, multi-turn conversations — built to your exact specifications.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">⟁</div>
      <h3>Agentic Workflows</h3>
      <p>Multi-step AI automations that handle real work: lead qualification, document processing, code review, support triage, data analysis, reporting. Claude does the job, not just the chat.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">⚡</div>
      <h3>Automation Pipelines</h3>
      <p>End-to-end pipelines connecting AI to your business processes. Trigger-based workflows, webhook integrations, scheduled tasks, and real-time processing — all production-grade.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">▶</div>
      <h3>Training & Onboarding</h3>
      <p>Hands-on training for your team so they actually use what we build. Prompt engineering, Claude Code workflows, MCP best practices, and documentation your team will reference daily.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- OPENCLAW / CLAWDBOT -->
<section id="clawdbot">
  <p class="section-label">// Personal AI Assistant</p>
  <h2 class="section-title">OpenClaw setup — your own AI that actually does things.</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">OpenClaw (ClawdBot) is the open-source personal AI assistant everyone's talking about. It runs on your hardware, connects to your messaging apps, and takes real actions. We set it all up for you.</p>

  <div class="services-grid">
    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">🦞</div>
      <h3>Full OpenClaw Setup</h3>
      <p>We install and configure OpenClaw on your Mac Mini, PC, or server — gateway, workspace, onboarding, skills, and daemon. Tuned for your workflow so it's production-ready from day one.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">💬</div>
      <h3>Channel Integration</h3>
      <p>Connect your assistant to WhatsApp, Telegram, Slack, Discord, Signal, iMessage, Microsoft Teams — or all of them. Same memory, same context, everywhere you already communicate.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">🧠</div>
      <h3>Custom Skills & Automations</h3>
      <p>We build custom skills for your assistant — email management, calendar automation, flight check-ins, smart home control, browser automation, financial tracking, and anything else you need it to do.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">⚙️</div>
      <h3>Voice, Canvas & Proactive Routines</h3>
      <p>Wake word activation, voice conversations via ElevenLabs, live Canvas workspace, cron-based routines — morning briefings, reminders, monitoring, and proactive alerts. Your assistant works even when you're not talking to it.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CALLPARK -->
<section id="callpark">
  <p class="section-label">// AI Receptionist</p>
  <h2 class="section-title">CallPark — never miss a call again.</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">An AI receptionist that answers your business phone 24/7, handles SMS, books appointments, and qualifies leads. Deployed and customized by us for your industry.</p>

  <div class="services-grid">
    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">☎</div>
      <h3>AI Phone Answering</h3>
      <p>Your CallPark receptionist picks up every call — after hours, overflow, weekends, holidays. It answers FAQs, captures caller details, and routes complex calls to your team. No hold music, no missed leads.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">📅</div>
      <h3>Appointment Booking</h3>
      <p>Callers book directly into your calendar over the phone or via text. Automated confirmations, rescheduling, and reminders — your schedule stays full without your team lifting a finger.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">💬</div>
      <h3>SMS Lead Qualification</h3>
      <p>Automated text conversations that engage leads, ask qualifying questions, and route hot prospects to your team. Works 24/7 and follows up automatically so no lead goes cold.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="service-card">
      <div class="service-icon">◈</div>
      <h3>Industry-Specific Setup</h3>
      <p>We configure CallPark for your exact business — real estate, dental, therapy, skincare, salons, law firms, and more. Custom scripts, personality, business hours, and integration with your existing tools.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW WE WORK -->
<section id="process">
  <p class="section-label">// How We Work</p>
  <h2 class="section-title">Embedded first. Build second.</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">We don't show up with a playbook. We learn your business from the inside, then architect a solution that actually fits.</p>

  <div class="process-timeline">
    <div class="process-step">
      <div class="process-marker">
        <span class="process-number">01</span>
        <div class="process-line"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-content">
        <div class="process-duration">Days 1–3</div>
        <h3>Discovery Embed</h3>
        <p>We spend 3 days inside your operation — on-site or remote. We shadow your team, map every tool, document every workflow, identify every bottleneck, and learn how your business actually runs. Not how you think it runs. How it <em>actually</em> runs.</p>
        <div class="process-details">
          <span>Tool & data flow audit</span>
          <span>Team workflow mapping</span>
          <span>Pain point identification</span>
          <span>Opportunity scoring</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="process-step">
      <div class="process-marker">
        <span class="process-number">02</span>
        <div class="process-line"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-content">
        <div class="process-duration">Days 4–5</div>
        <h3>Architecture & Planning</h3>
        <p>We take everything we learned and design your custom AI implementation plan — which MCP connections, what workflows to automate, where ClawdBot fits, what API integrations you need, and the exact order to build it all. You approve the blueprint before we write a line of code.</p>
        <div class="process-details">
          <span>Custom architecture design</span>
          <span>MCP connection map</span>
          <span>Workflow automation plan</span>
          <span>Implementation timeline</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="process-step">
      <div class="process-marker">
        <span class="process-number">03</span>
        <div class="process-line"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-content">
        <div class="process-duration">Weeks 2–3</div>
        <h3>Build & Deploy</h3>
        <p>We execute the plan — fast. Claude Code configured, MCP servers connected, ClawdBot deployed, automation pipelines live, API integrations wired up. Everything tested in your real environment with your real data before we call it done.</p>
        <div class="process-details">
          <span>Environment configuration</span>
          <span>Integration & automation build</span>
          <span>QA with real data</span>
          <span>Production deployment</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="process-step">
      <div class="process-marker">
        <span class="process-number">04</span>
      </div>
      <div class="process-content">
        <div class="process-duration">Weeks 3–5</div>
        <h3>Launch, Train & Support</h3>
        <p>We train your team hands-on — not a slide deck, real working sessions. Then we stick around for 2 weeks post-launch to fix anything, tune workflows, and answer every question. You're never left figuring it out alone.</p>
        <div class="process-details">
          <span>Team training sessions</span>
          <span>Custom documentation</span>
          <span>2-week support window</span>
          <span>Optimization & tuning</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top:3rem;">
    <p style="font-size:0.95rem;color:var(--light-gray);line-height:1.7;max-width:600px;">Infrastructure and hardware needs (dedicated machines, cloud resources, etc.) are scoped during discovery and billed separately at cost + 15%.</p>
  </div>
</section>

